      "content": "okay sounds manageable. i have some old ibuprofen in my cabinet too, would it be okay to take a couple of those with the cream to help with the warmth and swelling? also, if it starts to look a bit more yellow but doesn't hurt too much, i'll just keep layering more cream on it until it clears up right?",
